{"tid":1815394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遲d我電視唔開TVB，警察係唔係會上門拉我","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T09:01:28.000Z","uid":188176,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f92c81e6a9833dc15d7f876a1d6398ac3166e7a0","tid":1815394,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"警方表示，有人涉嫌在網上恐嚇一些公司不可在某機構賣廣告，警方指有公司已經報警，由網絡安全及科技罪案調查科跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科警司劉肇邦稱：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最近有人在網上鼓吹在網上抵制理念不同的店舖，如果有公司在某間電視台或在某些車站賣廣告就要抵制</span></span>，甚至狙擊他們產品，甚至有人發帖文，點名威脅某些公司要在限期前停止在某間電視台賣廣告，否則就會對相關公司發動攻勢。這種威脅的手段是黑社會常用的滅聲手法，他們向商戶施壓，脅迫他們就範。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedecffdce910a1d3282e10dd1e517b71fa4f60f","tid":1815394,"uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港係最自由經濟體系wo<br />\n我d錢唔洗係紅色企業就要比人拉<br />\n唔知黑驚係唔係收左黑錢幫手做野呢？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9df5ecd67832de1b851eb2c329f4638db6e124","tid":1815394,"uid":194298,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"無刑事成分，你查條撚咩，唔幫襯你都犯法呀? 出糧自動入錢落你戶口好無? 阿蛇你咁就係恐嚇我喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97390897fe8312b3a198a7a4ab3123b22252db54","tid":1815394,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:05:28.000Z",